**Banisher** | Extra Elected | Haunted
__Basics__
Each day, the Banisher may decide whether a banishment will take place during the next night. There may not be banishments in successive nights. 
__Details__
The Banisher may choose to resign at any point during a phase, but will only lose the role at the end of the phase.
Choosing a banishment is an immediate action. 
The Banisher gains an additional secret channel, which is reused for any subsequent Banishers.

__Simplified__
The Banisher is elected before the poltergeist and the banshee.
They may decide whether a banishment will take place, but may not decide on banishments on successive  days.

__Formalized__
TBD

__Card__
The Banisher is elected to lead the graveyard.
